            "descriptionRaw": "Perform a secret rite, entering the \"Twilight Meditation\" state, during which Sethos's Normal Attacks will be converted into enemy-piercing <color=#FFD780FF>Dusk Bolts</color>: Deal <color=#FFACFFFF>Electro DMG</color> to opponents in its path, with DMG increased based on Sethos's Elemental Mastery.\nSethos cannot perform Aimed Shots while in this state.\nDMG dealt by Dusk Bolts is considered Charged Attack DMG.\nThis effect will be canceled when Sethos leaves the field.\n\n<i>The archives of the Temple of Silence preserve many tomes left behind by Akhtamun, from the era of King Deshret. Many secret rituals of great power are recorded within, but even among the Temple of Silence, very few could master them.</i>",
            "name": "Secret Rite: Twilight Shadowpiercer"
        },
